{"tid":921768,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《新喜劇之王》賀歲迎豬年 周星馳摺櫈都出埋","createTime":"2018-11-29T23:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T01:22:51.000Z","uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b96307996e14dd58388ba1e1ffe7d1f67d0ab30e","tid":921768,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.gq.com.tw/_rs/645/userfiles/sm/sm1024_images_A1/37994/2018112983129137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.gq.com.tw%2F_rs%2F645%2Fuserfiles%2Fsm%2Fsm1024_images_A1%2F37994%2F2018112983129137.jpg&h=bbf232e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 各位觀眾！大家還記得那句最賺人熱淚的經典台詞：「其實我是一個演員。」嗎？是的，我們最期待的星爺周星馳，終於回來了！<br />\n他的導演新作品《新喜劇之王》公布首波手繪視覺，畫面上的背影身穿白雪公主服及高跟鞋，手拿「七大武器之首」的好折凳，身邊白鴿及樹葉飛舞，完全是超級英雄登場，劇力萬均的氣勢！<br />\n<br />\n今年香港賀歲檔電影好熱鬧，周星馳作品《新喜劇之王》於2019大年初一迎新歲，1999年的《喜劇之王》在20年後以全新姿態登場。近年來周星馳拍攝了多部特效大片，叫座之餘也讓不少人懷念他早期那些不加修飾的純喜劇元素。其實星爺早在三年前就開始創作新作的劇本，同時也在尋找合適演員，直到一切都準備就緒，這才著手開拍《新喜劇之王》。<br />\n<br />\n最新發布一張有趣的手繪先導海報：還記得1996年的《食神》中：「摺櫈的奧妙就在於它能隱藏於民居之中，唾手可得，平時還可以坐着它來隱藏殺機，就算被警察抓到也告不了你，真不愧為七種武器之首！」<br />\n<br />\n所以海報上是一個看似人所熟悉的卡通人物背影，手拿摺櫈擺出「唯我獨尊」架勢，白鴿與樹葉在周圍飛舞，「周星馳作品」五個大字，已令人期待！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.gq.com.tw/_rs/645/userfiles/sm/sm1024_images_A1/37994/2018112983088241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.gq.com.tw%2F_rs%2F645%2Fuserfiles%2Fsm%2Fsm1024_images_A1%2F37994%2F2018112983088241.jpg&h=04e4038a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.gq.com.tw/_rs/645/userfiles/sm/sm1024_images_A1/37994/2018112983088225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.gq.com.tw%2F_rs%2F645%2Fuserfiles%2Fsm%2Fsm1024_images_A1%2F37994%2F2018112983088225.jpg&h=f3b474fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.gq.com.tw/_rs/645/userfiles/sm/sm1024_images_A1/37994/2018112983101161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.gq.com.tw%2F_rs%2F645%2Fuserfiles%2Fsm%2Fsm1024_images_A1%2F37994%2F2018112983101161.jpg&h=61f201f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1543507841316&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1543507841316%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181130&d=%2FWF5AIj6jbqjK091Au4%2FB1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=5d417cde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1543507841316%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181130&h=ccfbb044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1543507841316&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181130</a>"},{"pid":"680e7a84aa035d76a59d5e509b2b01d44e121958","tid":921768,"uid":208940,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:27:23.000Z","msg":"大家陸演員王寶強做尹天仇，真係接受唔到"},{"pid":"cbbde82d7706b7aac3e096d996e9f3761d16f101","tid":921768,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:33:26.000Z","msg":"豬年賀歲片<br />\n周星馳一套<br />\n林敏聰一套<br />\n王祖藍一套<br />\n彭浩翔一套<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係睇Lego 2 算...."},{"pid":"d61108241c78deb6223562a2ed5c0317cf38eb66","tid":921768,"uid":98289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:35:16.000Z","msg":"九成九充滿大陸式笑話<br />\n點會好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc02b596b021bc019d2a00d608b6f5ad9b88082a","tid":921768,"uid":84081,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:35:37.000Z","msg":"睇住周星馳making of 仲吸引過睇班大陸蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6014dde2dfcd8eed3a730a6f23fe42de93dc30","tid":921768,"uid":30022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:34:19.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"c74fa49e4ec5301f922d902769b1c4b8020dff69","tid":9